  ('heelevel3-704caaf1-moex-00073', 'heelevel3-704caaf1', 'heelevel3-704caaf1-moex-111-67b07c2c', 'sub-heelevel3-704caaf1-04', NULL, 'essay', '病毒性出血熱（viralhemorrhagicfever）以發燒及出血為典型病徵，有些
