中，三大類主要的模式辨識受體與其作用機制，並詳述發炎小體
（inflammasome）是如何被刺激產生及作用。（20分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e0ec3af531a7", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "361", "s": "2209", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "醫用微生物及免疫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "五", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "衛生技術"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-704caaf1-moex-00077', 'heelevel3-704caaf1', 'heelevel3-704caaf1-moex-110-9bd893ac', 'sub-heelevel3-704caaf1-05', NULL, 'essay', '健康促進理論在了解個人是否會採取有益健康的健康行為時，常會依跨
